    {
      "id": "5a93c517_6c597a59",
      "file_path": "policy-management/src/test/java/org/onap/policy/drools/controller/DroolsControllerFactoryTest.java",
      "patchset_number": 2,
      "line": 76,
      "message": "I see, I was referring to the \"NullController\" (vs the \"MavenController\") that both implement the same controller interface :).     At some point I have to add \"MavenController\" junits and an \"assertMavenController\" that may make more clear.   I can accompany it with some comment to make it more clear.   That will come in future reviews.",
